sentence.text: In summary, a 15-lncRNA expression signature (BAIAP2-AS1, RP11-203J24.8, LINC01133, RP1-7G5.6, RP11-147L13.15, SERHL, CTC-537E7.3, RP11-440L14.1, RP11-131N11.4, ILF3-AS1, RP11-80H18.4, RP11-1096G20.5, CTD-2192J16.26, RP11-621L6.3, and RP11-571M6.18) were identified and validated which can predict cervical cancer patient survival.
